	bool "Rockchip Camera Engine for SoC with ISP1"
	help
	  Rockchip camera engine for SoC with ISP1, e.g.
	  RK3288, RK3399, RK3326, PX30, RK1808 etc.

if BR2_PACKAGE_CAMERA_ENGINE_RKISP
